To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private ShortLineCandle _shortlinecandle;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_shortlinecandle = ShortLineCandle(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_shortlinecandle.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "shortlinecandle", _shortlinecandle.Current.Value);
}
